he'd find financial success quickly; that my grandfather might send for her, her husband, and her younger son<U+0097>my great-grandfather and my great-uncle.

Text:

If he'd stay ok.
If he'd find happiness.

I would give everything<U+0097>my own life included<U+0097>for my child's safety. But I'd want to know he'd be ok.

Text:

Then he was in Nuremberg, where translated for nazis.

He defended freedom in Korea.
